rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0001
rows.name:
To think I could've stowed away on the
ship to earn myself some coin in Iira!
Well, it's too late now...

rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0002
rows.name: ...Uck! Did I say that out loud?

rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, it doesn't matter. I'm on the
straight and narrow now anyhow...

rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I've been living alone for a long time
now...and I've done some pretty bad
things.

rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0005
rows.name:
It's tough for a little girl to grow
up by herself here in Gula.

rows.label: tlk70000121_04_msg0006
rows.name:
But if you think you can turn things
around, I think I can dare to dream too,
just a little!
